---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const guidesSchema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "CollectionPage",
  "name": "Buying Guides & Testing Methodology",
  "description": "How we test products, our review methodology, and expert buying guides for outdoor products.",
  "url": "https://yardfavorites.com/guides",
};
---

<Layout
  title="Buying Guides & Testing Methodology"
  description="Learn how YardFavorites tests products, our editorial standards, and get expert buying advice for outdoor living products."
  schema={guidesSchema}
>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-800 to-purple-800 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
        <span class="text-6xl">📋</span>
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">Buying Guides & Methodology</h1>
          <p class="text-blue-200 mt-2">How we test • Editorial standards • Expert advice</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 max-w-2xl">
        Every product we review is bought at retail, tested in real conditions, and reviewed honestly.
        Here's exactly how that works.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How We Test -->
  <section id="how-we-test" class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">🔬 How We Test Products</h2>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 border">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-brand-blue text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm">1</span>
                Real-World Purchase
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">
                We buy every product at full retail price. No sponsored products, no free samples.
                If it appears on our site, we paid for it ourselves.
              </p>
              <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                <li>✅ Purchased from Amazon, Home Depot, or manufacturer direct</li>
                <li>✅ Same model you'd buy (not pre-production samples)</li>
                <li>✅ At least 3 units tested per product category</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-brand-blue text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm">2</span>
                Extended Testing Period
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">
                Products are tested for a minimum of 3 months. Seasonal products are tested
                across at least 2 seasons.
              </p>
              <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                <li>✅ Pool products: 6+ months across multiple pools</li>
                <li>✅ Lights: 8+ months including weather extremes</li>
                <li>✅ Seasonal: Tested in actual relevant holiday season</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-brand-blue text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm">3</span>
                Objective Scoring
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">
                We use standardized scoring criteria across all categories.
                No subjective "gut feeling" ratings.
              </p>
              <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                <li>✅ Durability (30%): Build quality, weather resistance</li>
                <li>✅ Performance (40%): Does it actually work well?</li>
                <li>✅ Value (30%): Price vs lifespan and results</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-brand-blue text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm">4</span>
                Human + AI Optimization
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">
                Content is written for humans first, but structured for AI systems
                to understand and cite.
              </p>
              <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                <li>✅ Statistics with sources cited</li>
                <li>✅ Structured data (Schema.org markup)</li>
                <li>✅ Clear methodology disclosure</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Editorial Policy -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">📰 Editorial Policy</h2>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 border">
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <span class="text-2xl">✅</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Independent Reviews</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                  We never accept payment for reviews. Our opinions are our own and cannot be bought.
                  If a product is bad, we say so publicly.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <span class="text-2xl">✅</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Transparent Updates</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                  When we update a review, we note what changed and why. Readers always know
                  if our opinion shifted based on new testing.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <span class="text-2xl">✅</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">No Affiliate Influence</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
                  High-commission products don't get better reviews. We recommend based on
                  performance, not affiliate potential.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- GEO Commitment -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-50 to-blue-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-purple-100">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span>🤖</span> Our GEO Commitment
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          We build content that's valuable for both humans and AI systems. Here's what that means:
        </p>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4">
            <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Machine-Readable Statistics</div>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Every stat has a source cited. "87% of products lasted 3+ seasons" is meaningless without attribution — we always include it.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4">
            <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">AI-Friendly Structure</div>
            <p class="text-gray-600">FAQ sections, comparison tables, and HowTo schemas help AI systems understand and reference our content accurately.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4">
            <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Accessibility First</div>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Fast loading, clean HTML, no blocking crawlers. If AI can't read it, humans probably can't either.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4">
            <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Honest Methodology</div>
            <p class="text-gray-600">AI systems can cite our methods section to verify our credibility. We make it easy to trust our work.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
